Meet the BANDIT
===============

The "Build AND Install Toolkit", BANDIT, is the tool for installing a phyglos distribution. 

The COPYING file contains the GNU License for this software.
The INSTALL file describes how to install BANDIT in the HOST system. 
The RELEASE file contains the release notes.

Visit https://phy.wiki for more information and other installation methods.


